<li id="cite_note-AllmusicHairMetal-2">^ <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicHairMetal_2-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicHairMetal_2-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicHairMetal_2-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicHairMetal_2-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicHairMetal_2-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicHairMetal_2-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.allmusic.com/explore/style/d2693">"Hair metal"</a>, <i>Allmusic</i>. Retrieved 6 July 2010.</li>
<li id="cite_note-AllmusicPopMetal-3">^ <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicPopMetal_3-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicPopMetal_3-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-AllmusicPopMetal_3-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.allmusic.com/explore/style/d7728">"Pop metal"</a>, <i>Allmusic</i>. Retrieved 6 July 2010.</li>
<li id="cite_note-Moore2009-4">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Moore2009_4-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Moore2009_4-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Moore2009_4-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Moore2009_4-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> R. Moore, <i>Sells Like Teen Spirit: Music, Youth Culture, and Social Crisis</i> (New York, NY: New York University Press, 2009), <a href="Special:BookSources/0814757480" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0814757480</a>, pp. 105-6.</li>
